{"tid":398384,"cid":21,"subCid":0,"title":"[hip hop]紅花會-PG One萬磁王討論區（one)","createTime":"2017-09-13T07:07:58.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-19T06:23:25.000Z","uid":5785,"like":19,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"b6ac1b7126dd4e96dda752efdd5f8ca7dfc057a5","tid":398384,"uid":5785,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-13T07:07:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/13/142830_6584ae686f41cf21860178d1d182f4fb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F13%2F142830_6584ae686f41cf21860178d1d182f4fb.jpg&h=4ecb8587&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">PGONE萬磁王個人資料　　<br />\n本名：王昊<br />\n<br />\n出生日期：1994年4月5日<br />\n<br />\n星座：白羊座<br />\n<br />\n暱稱：PG_ONE萬磁王/皮幾萬<br />\n<br />\n出身地：黑龍江哈爾濱<br />\n<br />\n團體：紅花會<br />\n<br />\n職業：Rappr 饒舌歌手 hip hop音樂製作人</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/13/145643_d8d8f44d2ca9c6a4d235641b88855f57.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F13%2F145643_d8d8f44d2ca9c6a4d235641b88855f57.jpg&h=f2f81cc9&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/13/145644_d8d8f44d2ca9c6a4d235641b88855f57.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F13%2F145644_d8d8f44d2ca9c6a4d235641b88855f57.jpg&h=070de56d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n簡介：PG ONE原名叫王昊，是黑龍江哈爾濱人，牡羊座，出身1994年的PG ONE給自己取名「萬磁王」，為中國西北HIP HOP團隊「紅花會」的固定成員，其團隊幕後還有專業的混音師，製作人，策劃人和宣傳媒體，是一個完整並多元化的說唱團體。pg one在說唱界是特別有競爭力的一位選手，曾經多次在各種Freestyle Battle比賽中奪得過冠軍。<br />\n2012年，參加了人生中第一個freestyle battle比賽同年，以Battle MC身份正式進入hip hop界。2013年，在Iron Mic長春賽區獲冠軍，接着又拿下多過Freestyle Battle比賽冠軍。2015年的PG One來到西安參加battle比賽，拿下全國總冠軍，加入了紅花會；同年，推出《New.P》、《中二病》等單曲。2016年，推出多首作品。2017年，参加Hip-hop音樂show《中國有嘻哈》的比賽，最終獲得全國總冠軍之一！<br />\n<br />\n作品:<br />\nPG One-Penta Kill<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/C30-n5AyGL4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FC30-n5AyGL4&d=Fiapx9xV0uLnJffjTeDtIghMEkA7P3Wv%2FuCJwdwWxT4%3D&h=d03d3cd5\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/C30-n5AyGL4</a><br />\n<br />\nPG One-中二病<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/DQAUe4cq8b8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FDQAUe4cq8b8&d=Fiapx9xV0uLnJffjTeDtIghMEkA7P3Wv%2FuCJwdwWxT4%3D&h=e232635c\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/DQAUe4cq8b8</a><br />\n<br />\nPG One-Junky Mouth<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/V3Sl2jEju-A\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FV3Sl2jEju-A&d=Fiapx9xV0uLnJffjTeDtIghMEkA7P3Wv%2FuCJwdwWxT4%3D&h=7ce88bae\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/V3Sl2jEju-A</a><br />\n<br />\nPG One-Fresh One<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/MIIx3bXIbjQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FMIIx3bXIbjQ&d=Fiapx9xV0uLnJffjTeDtIghMEkA7P3Wv%2FuCJwdwWxT4%3D&h=a21e49c2\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/MIIx3bXIbjQ</a><br />\n<br />\nPG One/BrAnT.B-地平線<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/XlUeiRlON7k\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FXlUeiRlON7k&d=Fiapx9xV0uLnJffjTeDtIghMEkA7P3Wv%2FuCJwdwWxT4%3D&h=b4ee5fb1\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/XlUeiRlON7k</a><br />\n<br />\nPG One-中二病live(現場型撚到喊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ）<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/FKz50IxsPjI\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FFKz50IxsPjI&d=Fiapx9xV0uLnJffjTeDtIghMEkA7P3Wv%2FuCJwdwWxT4%3D&h=bff20d10\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/FKz50IxsPjI</a>"},{"pid":"bb3e05d4d69028acff8f1b5e1da6d2f98a6a8b9f","tid":398384,"uid":5785,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-13T07:37:58.000Z","msg":"另外介紹幾首紅花會遍R&amp;B風格嘅歌，都做得幾好！<br />\n紅花會-蛻變<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/-9GQqDWsy6U\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F-9GQqDWsy6U&d=